'''凱爾·霍華德·里滕豪斯'''（{{Lang-en|'''Kyle Howard Rittenhouse'''}}，{{Bd|2003年|1月3日|catIdx=R}}），美國[[伊利諾伊州|伊利諾伊州]]人。他於2020年8月25日在[[威斯康星州|威斯康星州]][[基諾沙暴亂|基諾沙暴亂]]示威中充當[[義警_(民間治安組織)|義警]]（vigilante）維持治安，與「[[Black_Lives_Matter|Black Lives Matter]]」示威者在兩個地點發生衝突，造成兩名試圖奪槍的示威者死亡，一名非法持槍且在衝突中拔槍指向他的示威者受傷。起初，部分左翼媒體和當時正在競選美國總統的[[拜登|祖·拜登]]將其稱為「[[白人優越主義|白人至上主義]]者」和「隨機射手」，部份媒體更把里滕豪斯的合法自衛行為說成「向人群掃射」等。然而，現場有多段影像證明兩名被射殺示威者先試圖搶奪凱爾的槍。一名被擊傷的示威者在法庭上承認「當我站在3至5米遠，槍口向天時，他沒開槍，直到我向他逼近，用槍指向他時，他才開槍」。2021年11月19日，他被[[基諾沙縣巡迴法院|基諾沙縣巡迴法院]]判定為正當防衛，處以無罪釋放。

==背景==
凱爾·里滕豪斯於2003年出生於[[伊利諾伊州|伊利諾伊州]]的[[安提阿|安提阿]]，他與母親溫蒂·里滕豪斯（Wendy Rittenhouse）一起生活在安提阿。在2017-18學年，他就讀了Lakes社區高中一個學期，此後沒有再重新註冊任何一家本地高中。法庭記錄顯示，一年前，他的母親以「13歲的惡霸稱呼她的兒子『愚蠢』，並恐嚇他」為由，為兒子-{里}-滕豪斯和他現年19歲的姐姐向警局申請了保護令。<ref>{{cite news  |last1=GROVES  |first1=STEPHEN  |title=Who is Kyle Rittenhouse?Teen accused of killing two and wounding another thrust into debate over protests  |url=https://lmtribune.com/northwest/who-is-kyle-rittenhouse/article_a8d44f51-8d3c-5cc6-9209-0aa49130fe66.html  |access-date=September 27, 2020  |work=The Lewiston Tribune  |date=2020-08-29|archive-date=2020-10-24  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024000541/https://lmtribune.com/northwest/who-is-kyle-rittenhouse/article_a8d44f51-8d3c-5cc6-9209-0aa49130fe66.html  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>在校外，里滕豪斯與安提阿消防局和[[葛雷斯雷克|葛雷斯雷克]]警察局一起參加了學員計劃，該計劃對14至21歲的青少年進行了執法基礎培訓。 <ref name="#1">{{cite news |last1=Armus |first1=Teo |title=Who is Kyle Rittenhouse? Here’s what we know about the 17-year-old charged in the Kenosha protest shooting. |url=https://www.boston.com/news/national-news-2/2020/08/27/who-is-kyle-rittenhouse |access-date=September 27, 2020 |work=Boston News |date=2020-08-27|archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204041739/https://www.boston.com/news/national-news-2/2020/08/27/who-is-kyle-rittenhouse |dead-url=no }}</ref>

里滕豪斯在伊利諾伊州[[林登赫斯特|林登赫斯特]]的[[YMCA|YMCA]]擔任兼職救生員。2020年3月，他因[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]而休假。<ref name="#1"/> 2020年1月30日，里滕豪斯參加了在[[得梅因|得梅因]]舉行的特朗普集會，坐在前排，並張貼了1月的[[TikTok|TikTok]]影片。<ref>{{cite news |last1=GROVES |first1=STEPHEN |title=Who is Kyle Rittenhouse? Teen accused of killing two and wounding another thrust into debate over protests |url=https://lmtribune.com/northwest/who-is-kyle-rittenhouse/article_a8d44f51-8d3c-5cc6-9209-0aa49130fe66.html |access-date=September 27, 2020 |work=The Lewiston Tribune |date=2020-08-29|archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024000541/https://lmtribune.com/northwest/who-is-kyle-rittenhouse/article_a8d44f51-8d3c-5cc6-9209-0aa49130fe66.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>里滕豪斯在青少年時代就支持聲援警察的“[[Blue_Lives_Matter|Blue Lives Matter]]”運動。

==在基諾沙抗議中射擊==
{{main|基諾沙騷亂槍擊案|基諾沙暴亂}}
2020年8月25日，在威斯康星州基諾沙右翼基諾沙衛隊民兵呼籲志願者在[[喬治·弗洛伊德|喬治·弗洛伊德]]（George Floyd）抗議活動中幫助保護本地企業免受BLM暴徒的干擾（在警察槍殺雅各布之後，蔓延至基諾沙）<ref>{{cite news |last1=News Partner |first1=Wisconsin Examiner States Newsroom |title=A 'Call To Arms' That Filled Kenosha With Combat Weapons |url=https://patch.com/wisconsin/mountpleasant/call-arms-filled-kenosha-combat-weapons |access-date=September 27, 2020 |work=Patch |date=2020-08-29 |archive-date=2021-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211117032358/https://patch.com/wisconsin/mountpleasant/call-arms-filled-kenosha-combat-weapons |dead-url=no }}</ref>，里滕豪斯前往基諾沙（Kenosha），他的辯護律師聲稱他曾到基諾沙（Kenosha）擔任救生員。輪班結束後，據說他和一個朋友決定清理當地的BLM塗鴉，包括反警察的口號。在當地企業主呼籲當地人幫助他保護自己的汽車經銷店之後，里滕豪斯和他的朋友說自己武裝好了，接了電話。<ref>{{cite news |last1=WIRE SERVICE |first1=CNN.com |title=Kenosha shooting suspect Kyle Rittenhouse called a friend to say he ‘killed somebody,’ police say, and then shot two others |url=https://www.mercurynews.com/2020/08/28/kenosha-shooting-suspect-kyle-rittenhouse-called-a-friend-to-say-he-killed-somebody-police-say-and-then-shot-two-others/ |access-date=September 27, 2020 |work=The Mercury News |date=2020-08-28|archive-date=2020-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219203441/https://www.mercurynews.com/2020/08/28/kenosha-shooting-suspect-kyle-rittenhouse-called-a-friend-to-say-he-killed-somebody-police-say-and-then-shot-two-others/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>他們與其他基諾沙警衛隊民兵在街上巡邏，以防止暴徒破壞私人財產。 36歲的基諾沙居民約瑟夫·羅森鮑姆（Joseph Rosenbaum）試圖從他手中搶走里滕豪斯的槍，導致里滕豪斯向他開槍。然後，抗議者將他追到一個停車場的停車場，他打電話給一個熟人，告訴他們他相信自己剛剛殺了一個人。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Karimi |first1=Faith |title=Kenosha shooting suspect called a friend to say he 'killed somebody,' police say, and then shot two others |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/08/28/us/kyle-rittenhouse-kenosha-shooting/index.html |access-date=September 27, 2020 |work=CNN |date=2020-08-29 |archive-date=2021-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211217201746/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/08/28/us/kyle-rittenhouse-kenosha-shooting/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>隨後他跑到大街上，有數人跟著追趕並大喊他剛剛開槍射人，里滕豪斯在追逐中跌倒，隨即有人對倒在地上的在里滕豪斯進行攻擊。其中一名抗議者安東尼·休伯（Anthony Huber）用滑板襲擊了里滕豪斯並企圖奪槍，里滕豪斯在搶奪間開槍擊中休伯胸部並導致其死亡。另一名傷者Gaige Grosskreutz最初將他的手舉到空中時並未受到攻擊，但右手拿了一把上了膛的GLOCK 27，且將雙手放下時繼續接近並將槍口朝向里滕豪斯，導致里滕豪斯開槍打傷了他。<ref>{{cite news |last1=and Scott Bauer |first1=Stephen Groves |title=Victims of Kenosha protest shooting tried to disarm Kyle Rittenhouse: Reports |url=https://abc7ny.com/kyle-rittenhouse-kenosha-shooting-jacob-blake/6393801/ |access-date=September 27, 2020 |work=Eyewitness News |date=2020-08-29|archive-date=2020-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206222401/https://abc7ny.com/kyle-rittenhouse-kenosha-shooting-jacob-blake/6393801/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>槍擊事件發生後警方趕到現場，里滕豪斯將手舉向空中並靠近警察，但警察僅警告-{里}-滕豪斯離開路面，里滕豪斯走向路肩後仍試圖靠近警車，車上警官卻仍舊沒有意識到他是剛剛射擊的槍手，最後在其中一名警官使用胡椒噴霧後里滕豪斯放棄繼續靠近並離開現場。<ref>{{cite news |last1=and EMILY CRANE |first1=KAREN RUIZ |title=Police-obsessed gunman, 17, who is charged with murder of two BLM protesters during Kenosha riots sat front row at a Trump MAGA rally as video interview emerges of him bragging about being a vigilante before the mayhem unfolded |url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8668207/Kyle-Rittenhouse-bragged-vigilante-inteview-shooting-Kenosha.html |access-date=September 27, 2020 |work=Daily Mail |date=2020-08-27 |archive-date=2022-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121212318/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8668207/Kyle-Rittenhouse-bragged-vigilante-inteview-shooting-Kenosha.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==被捕及受審==
里滕豪斯回到他母親在安條克的家中，在第二天凌晨也就是8月26日自行前往警局自首，並且立即被逮捕。根據威斯康星州法律，因為當時他已經17歲，所以將被視為成人起訴，該起訴列出了六項刑事指控。其中包括了一級過失殺人罪，是因為殺了羅森鮑姆， 一級肆意危害安全罪， 一級故意殺人罪，是因為槍殺了胡貝爾， 一級故意殺人未遂是因為打中了克魯伊茨的胳膊， 未滿18 歲持有危險武器。但是這個未滿18歲持有危險武器罪後來在庭審時被法官施羅德駁回了，理由是里滕豪斯的辯護律師指出了該州法律是允許未成年人持有16寸槍管以上的長槍的。<ref>{{Cite web|title=17-year-old arrested after 2 killed during unrest in Kenosha|url=https://apnews.com/97a0700564fb52d7f664d8de22066f88|accessdate=2020-08-27|author=Householder|first=Mike, and Scott Bauer|work=Associated Press|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826104020/https://apnews.com/97a0700564fb52d7f664d8de22066f88|archivedate=2020-08-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>  他的法律小組辯稱，他是為了自衛而行動，並被錯誤逮捕，並且他與一個暴徒進行了鬥爭。<ref>{{Cite web|title='Enough Is Enough': CovCath Attorney Lin Wood Offers to Help Kyle Rittenhouse For Free After GoFundMe Shuts Down Legal Defense Fund "If Kyle cannot defend himself under the circumstances shown in videos, we are all at risk."|url=http://www.informationliberation.com/?id=61681|accessdate=2020-08-27|author=Menahan, Chris|date=2020-08-27|archive-date=2020-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827123733/http://www.informationliberation.com/?id=61681|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Lawyer for accused Kenosha shooter Kyle Rittenhouse demands ‘justice’|url=https://nypost.com/2020/08/27/lawyer-for-kenosha-shooter-kyle-rittenhouse-demands-justice-for-kyle|accessdate=2020-08-27|author=Fitz-Gibbon, Jorge|date=2020-08-27|publisher=New York Post|archive-date=2020-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827221532/https://nypost.com/2020/08/27/lawyer-for-kenosha-shooter-kyle-rittenhouse-demands-justice-for-kyle/|dead-url=no}}</ref>總統[[唐納德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200902/s00014/1598984153068/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%92%90%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%80%85-%E7%A8%B1%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B5%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E5%B1%AC%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B|title=特朗普撐支持者 稱民兵開槍屬自衛|accessdate=2020-12-17|archive-date=2020-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902031239/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200902/s00014/1598984153068/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%92%90%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%80%85-%E7%A8%B1%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B5%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E5%B1%AC%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[塔克·卡森|塔克·卡爾森]]等主要保守派為里滕豪斯辯護。8月28日，法官宣布將里滕豪斯的引渡日期推遲至9月25日。於10月30日，里滕豪斯被伊州法院裁定引渡其到威斯康辛州受審，不得被釋放。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.shijiebobao.com/shownew/2/299934.html|title=世界播:凯尔·里滕豪斯将被引渡到威斯康星州}}{{Dead link}}</ref>在11月23日，里滕豪斯獲得由右翼組織支付的200萬美元保釋金而獲得保釋。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN2802RR|title=Teen charged in Kenosha shootings released on $2 million bond, sheriff's office says|accessdate=2021-11-21|archive-date=2021-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211121225237/https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN2802RR|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.npr.org/2020/11/20/937323873/kyle-rittenhouse-released-on-2-million-bail-awaiting-trial-in-kenosha-wis-deaths|title=Kyle Rittenhouse Released On $2 Million Bail, Awaiting Trial In Kenosha, Wis., Deaths|accessdate=2021-11-21|archive-date=2022-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120231847/https://www.npr.org/2020/11/20/937323873/kyle-rittenhouse-released-on-2-million-bail-awaiting-trial-in-kenosha-wis-deaths|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nbcchicago.com/news/local/kyle-rittenhouse-released-from-kenosha-county-jail-after-2m-bond-posted/2377086/|title=Kyle Rittenhouse Released From Kenosha County Jail After Bond Posted: Sheriff's Office|accessdate=2021-11-21|archive-date=2021-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211122002850/https://www.nbcchicago.com/news/local/kyle-rittenhouse-released-from-kenosha-county-jail-after-2m-bond-posted/2377086/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2021年11月19日，[[基諾沙縣巡迴法院|基諾沙縣巡迴法院]]陪審團裁定所有指控均不成立，宣判凱爾·里滕豪斯無罪釋放。州檢方無法上訴，意味這是最終裁決<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kyle Rittenhouse found not guilty on all charges|url=https://amp.cnn.com/cnn/us/live-news/kyle-rittenhouse-trial-verdict-watch-11-19-21/index.html|accessdate=2020-11-20|author=Adrienne Vogt, Aditi Sangal, Meg Wagner, Melissa Macaya and Melissa Mahtani|date=2020-11-19|publisher=CNN|7=|language=en|archive-date=2021-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211201081032/https://amp.cnn.com/cnn/us/live-news/kyle-rittenhouse-trial-verdict-watch-11-19-21/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國總統[[乔·拜登|祖·拜登]]則呼籲公眾尊重並接受陪審團的裁決。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Biden reacts to Rittenhouse verdict: 'The jury system works, and we have to abide by it'|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/11/19/politics/joe-biden-kyle-rittenhouse-verdict/index.html|access-date=2021-11-22|last=Carvajal|first=Nikki|work=CNN|archive-date=2021-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211121003508/https://www.cnn.com/2021/11/19/politics/joe-biden-kyle-rittenhouse-verdict/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
